  "description": "SCORE2-Diabetes estimates the 10-year risk of fatal and non-fatal cardiovascular disease (myocardial infarction, stroke, CVD death) in European adults aged 40-69 with type 2 diabetes and without prior CVD. Source: SCORE2-Diabetes Working Group, ESC Cardiovascular Risk Collaboration. Eur Heart J 2023;44(28):2544-2556.",
